      "para_id": "Q000917.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) For Ninĝirsu , the powerful warrior of Enlil , Gudea , ruler of Lagaš , who built Ninĝirsu's E-ninnu , built and restored his spectacular Kasura gate , which brings abundance ."
